HEADWORD: Ampliate
<hw>Am"pli*ate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ampliatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>ampliare</ets> to make wider, fr.
<ets>amplus</ets>. See <er>Ample</er>.]</ety> <def>To enlarge.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To maintain and <qex>ampliate</qex> the external possessions of
your empire.</q> <rj><qau>Udall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ampliate</ent>⟦br⟧

